file_content.text: Hmph. This isn't even an army, it's a rabble!
This army is puny. Should have died under droid's feet.
Hardly even worth our time, really. Let's get this over with.
No matter. They will die here, under ours.
Still want a fight, huh? Let's give 'em one!
Now we fight together. You will be crushed!
You are fools to challenge us together. Now see why!
Republic, Imperial, doesn't matter. Bring it on!
Should have run. Too late now!
I hunt food bigger than you!
First blood will be mine!
We don't accept surrender!
My people aren't known as fighters. Gives us an edge.
Only strongest in tribe become Spearmaster!
I do not call my army immortal. Our enemies do.
Fought for the Republic once. Now I choose my battles.
No one sees this move coming. Almost seems unfair.
Ancient tribal strategy. Never fails.
Enough play. Let's show them our strength!
Some things you only learn in the field. Here's one of 'em.
Ugh! I'm not going out like this!
Ancestors, give me strength!
Pain is nothing. I cannot be killed!
I'm a war vet. Few scratches aren't gonna stop me!
It took an army to kill me. Remember that!
Death comes. I go.
This is how a warrior dies.
Killed in action... sounds about right.
